primio te poruke?

197
00:22:12,749 --> 00:22:14,418
Ford, F-o-r-d. Halo? Trenutak.

198
00:22:26,346 --> 00:22:28,557
Da li je Dejmon unutra?

199
00:22:39,359 --> 00:22:41,904
ta se deava, momci, kako je?

200
00:22:42,738 --> 00:22:45,908
Lep auto, kako je ?

201
00:22:47,701 --> 00:22:51,038
Drago mi je. -Samo trenutak, mogu te
zvati kasnije?

202
00:22:53,665 --> 00:22:57,628
Brinuo sam da nee doi, ovde sam..

203
00:22:57,961 --> 00:23:01,548
Hoe autogram? -Ne, ne, zna 11 sati..

204
00:23:02,007 --> 00:23:05,177
Ford, dogovorili smo sastanak u 11 sati..

205
00:23:06,178 --> 00:23:09,723
Ja imam sastanak u 11, ali ne sa tobom.
