261
00:30:13,146 --> 00:30:17,776
Snimila sam Baha, Betovenov koncert i
njegove sonate.

262
00:30:17,776 --> 00:30:18,527
Sve u izvoenju Glen Gula?

263
00:30:18,527 --> 00:30:22,531
Veinu. Ne postoji njihov snimak
Betovena,tako da..

264
00:30:22,781 --> 00:30:27,077
Draga Mari Anela, ako vam potraim
Mercedes, da li bi doneli Linkolna?

265
00:30:27,286 --> 00:30:32,666
