332
00:36:05,624 --> 00:36:08,377
Stvarno interesantno.
-Kako je to interesantno?

333
00:36:10,087 --> 00:36:13,799
Pa, postavlja neka interesantna pitanja..

334
00:36:14,758 --> 00:36:20,138
